# Dynallery version 0.1

Very, Very, Very Open For Everyone!

We was created the "poor" javascript coding but with excellent concept for Advance gallery. It's concept like Google Images.
You can see how this work, please enjoy. 

If you want contribute in this project, let us know you fork this project first. 
Set the comfort chair and please bring your fresh algorithm idea into Dynallery project. 

We combine Dynallery Project with jQuery jPages v0.7 [Check it out](http://luis-almeida.github.com/jPages)
